Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:26.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Want a walnut?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:38.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is starting to get interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get any sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:37.55,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow of Albion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.24,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've requested approval from headquarters \Nfor the observation and protection subjects
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,on this base to wear these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So it's time to correct our past mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you freeing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:14.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm correcting our mistake. \NI cleared this with HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:18.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Use of Lead Gears on this base is now forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:24.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As Globe's observer organization, \NSalty Dog cannot allow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The commander's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:36.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My opinion of him just improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I will introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is Akari Yomatsuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's the daughter of the commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,who lived with his wife after they split...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His wife is Governor Yomatsuri, \Naboard the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.52,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the magical girl Akari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Magical girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.69,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're the girl from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she is Code Papillon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,last night's flight director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She is also an amazingly talented hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She was good enough to try hacking Alonzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to not have her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've been planning to have her \Ncooperate with us for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Akari's a hacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:37.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:46.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,How could he be so cruel to the daughter \Nhe hasn't seen for five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't seen her for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My opinion of him just dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:53.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,How did li'l ol' me end up a magical girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.10,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,"Li'l ol' me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.19,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a bumpkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.74,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My father is the commander of \NGlobe's Tanegashima base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:02.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,And my mother is governor of \Nthe satellite base {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:05.21,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My parents, concerned only \Nwith their jobs, abandoned me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:07.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,and I was always so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:11.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My computer was my only friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.02,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Four years ago, I was so excited
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:22.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,that my father was going to spend \Nmy birthday with me for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason for his last-second cancellation is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:28.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,that he actually had a date \Nwith Rita-san right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, s-s-see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:33.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We had to recruit her for this \Nbase as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My opinion of him just plummeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.41,SignA,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Annou Yams
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.41,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Annou Yams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.08,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping you locked in the base all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.64,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Will you allow me to recruit her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.69,Default - flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm not cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.28,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:26.78,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But she'll stay at my place, \Nalong with the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.55,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean Teppei and Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:34.08,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,As well as Daichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.91,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I should have done this sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:45.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so grateful that Daichi made me realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The wind on this island feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is this you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.23,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.80,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and Uncle Nishikubo were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:13.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,So when I was little, I used to stay here a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:16.08,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I loved this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.81,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.72,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're cuter when you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.27,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you're family, \Nand this is your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:51.78,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But you're growing boys and girls \Nliving beneath the same roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.86,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So try to show some restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:58.94,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:02.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Was the cologne in the bathroom \Na present from Rita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.94,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about small things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you a small person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.14,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.80,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the switch for the steam bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.51,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,My restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.55,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Restraint...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.15,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,She has me beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally in the lead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.02,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way this house smells!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.80,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It smells old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But it's got heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:36.97,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a friend of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like the walnut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.69,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You know Pitz?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him at the shrine today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:48.54,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,On this island, there's an old shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a legend about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:58.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, a messenger descended from \Nheaven, leaving behind a huge rock
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,with an angel sealed inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:05.84,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:10.65,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think is a stronger heroine, \Na magical girl or an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:17.08,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many stars, \NI can't find the Big Dipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This island has barely any streetlamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.94,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It really is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Milky Way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.83,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Milky Way's amazing too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.27,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Just two days ago, I was wondering \Nwhat to do with my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.72,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's all amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.47,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to that rainbow you showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:43.97,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That round rainbow... I always thought \Nit was something I'd imagined as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it creep you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.19,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You always surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:09.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your Livlaster really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.30,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the game's back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:22.76,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow Daichi Manatsu \Nto go on any further missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:31.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was the Globe Federation's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,unanimous opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Doghouse to Pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that the Daichi Manatsu boy defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,the Kiltgang with his Livlaster \Nis having a significant effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:04.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But Impacters other than the Earth \NEngine are also capable of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:09.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Globe is investigating the use of \Nlow-orbit Impacters, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think eliminating them at close range, \Nin the stratosphere, is the more reliable way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't that risk damaging \Nthe planet's surface too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:16.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We are past that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Mutou is absolutely necessary \Nto the Kivotos Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that having her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:28.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,under our control is a top priority \Nfor those of us in the Ark Faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:32.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, it will be up to you to \Ndeal with Daichi Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi Manatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:46.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Selling the basic theory behind the Machine \NGoodfellows and the designer children
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,would be enough to earn a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And CEO Kube gets everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:58.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But it was the A.I. called Puck that \Ndeveloped the basic theory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.16,Default,Hi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.58,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Your secretary, Hitomi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:14.29,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,is totally in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.55,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you make her yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.30,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Have any Kiltgang attacked since the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:25.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that manned Impacter \Nis called the Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.72,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, I kicked its butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If it was running off a Livlaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,does that mean they can use \Nthe Princess of Blume now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.92,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Approaching-Earth Object sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Kiltgang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.85,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's been nine years since I last \Nturned into the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, I underestimated the Earthlings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.24,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:28.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Type-1 that killed Daichi Manatsu's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:39.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A Kiltgang has appeared within \Ndefensive zone 1, Alpha sector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading straight for Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Distance 34,000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Approach speed 52 meters per second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:51.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,They want a report about when I got the \NLivlaster, but I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.61,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:11.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold, Daichi Manatsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Kiltgang has attacked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:19.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.00,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.79,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,the type that appeared nine years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's the same one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:43.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:46.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Alonzo has approved an emergency \Nlaunch of the Earth Engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're launching the Pegasus rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine's energy is charging!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:15.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.77,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I've forbidden Daichi to launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I gave him permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Governor, the expansion sequence \Nhas activated again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi Manatsu-kun has already won one battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:38.20,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Kiltgang that's currently approaching Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.83,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,is the one that killed your father nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, \Nlaunching the Earth Engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:03.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done any maintenance yet, \Nbeyond swapping out armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:16.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But if the need arises, \Nwe have the low-orbit Impacters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:17.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're overstepping your authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:18.80,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:24.40,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I am denying Salty Dog access to the \Ncontrol room or any of the secure blocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for Daichi Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:47.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.16,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, Alpha sector's \NImpacters aren't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:55.97,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:59.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The relay satellite that sends \Nthe commands isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can try bouncing it off another satellite...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.72,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to the magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:05.98,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Logical, logical...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,German Impacters, you will do as I command!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Logical"? That isn't magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Impacter Feige's interception \Nsystems are coming on line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:21.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Akari's doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:25.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's controlling the German Impacters from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're a lot more lax than the Thousand \Nsystem I took over a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.79,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:36.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You were behind the hacking of the \NAmerican Air Force last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about small things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you a small person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.72,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:47.32,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A voice that resounds throughout infinity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:52.31,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sings a melody of gentle memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:19:02.28,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The light of the promise \NI know we once shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:56.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Its epicenter is Tanegashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I won't underestimate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Impacter Feige, lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine is coming into \Ncontact with the Kiltgang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine still isn't repaired!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.02,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.34,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,My dad flew to stop that thing, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.98,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That means I have to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.58,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.12,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,what my dad did will be meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.63,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get any farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.74,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving so slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been repaired at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:17.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rip you apart with my fangs, Earth Engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:24.57,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.03,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A planetary sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Albion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:57.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Albion... What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.95,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That Kiltgang...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.26,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:27.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.60,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:05.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:07.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:11.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This thing's main system never worked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:14.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it turn on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That earthquake was Blume moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:24.92,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I just sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:28.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:33.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's thanks to God that we survived today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:36.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,God?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:42.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:17.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei was able to pilot an enemy robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:19.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:23.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Globe's Tanegashima base is split \Nover Teppei's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.01,0:24:27.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And then, two of the enemy launch a bold assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:31.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 4 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.44,0:24:33.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Assault of the Planetary Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:33.99,Title2,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Assault of the Planetary Gear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.52,0:24:37.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
